org.gradoop.temporal.model.impl.operators.aggregation.functions

Class AbstractTimeAggregateFunction

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.aggregation.functions.BaseAggregateFunction
      • org.gradoop.temporal.model.impl.operators.aggregation.functions.AbstractTimeAggregateFunction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, AggregateFunction, TemporalAggregateFunction
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MaxTime, MinTime

    public abstract class AbstractTimeAggregateFunction
extends BaseAggregateFunction
implements TemporalAggregateFunction
    An abstract super class for aggregation functions that aggregate a time of a temporal element. Times can be a TimeDimension.Field of a TimeDimension.
    See Also:
